              <span id="reviewTextContainer2936152162" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15216891946330891983">When looking at it separate, it is a 4 star book. Well written, well established, and brings you into this world that is different, thinks different and comes to different conclusions than you are used to...<br/>As a book two in a quartet, I am hellish confused... What? Where? When? Why? I hope it will be explained in the books to come but right now I am just confused...</span>

